<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yǐ sè liè a nǐ yào tīng zhe 迦南952</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǐ sè liè a nǐ yào tīng zhe yé hé huá shì dú yī zhēn shén.
 chuàng zào tiān de wàn wù, guǎn lǐ yǔ zhòu wàn yǒu jiù shì zhēn shén yé hé huá.
 nǐ bù kě bài ǒu xiàng, yě bù kě tí bié shén de míng.
 nǐ yī shēng yào dān dān shì fèng tā yǐ jìng wèi tā wèi zhì bǎo.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>952</hymn_number>
</song>